			"detail": "Define chord diagram (top-of-score list)",
			"documentation": "Define a chord diagram for the list at the top of the score. For inline chord names above each beat, use {ch \"ChordName\"} on that beat.",
			"insertText": "\\chord \"${1}\""
		}
	],
